---
---

<section id="selection-process" class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-[min(100vw,768px)] max-w-screen-xl mx-auto fade-in-up">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-4 tracking-tight">Tahapan Seleksi</h2>
            <p class="text-subtle text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Pahami setiap tahapan agar Anda tidak melewatkan kesempatan emas ini.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14">
            <!-- Coding Camp Process -->
            <div class="bg-surface p-6 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-subtle-light shadow-sm hover:shadow-hover-premium transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                     <div class="h-10 w-2.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
                     <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 tracking-tight">Coding Camp 2.0</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-10 relative">
                     <!-- Connection line -->
                     <div class="absolute left-[1.15rem] top-10 bottom-10 w-0.5 bg-slate-100 hidden sm:block"></div>
                     
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/20 bg-white text-primary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm">1</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Isi Formulir Aplikasi</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Lengkapi formulir pendaftaran dengan data diri Anda secara lengkap dan benar. Pastikan untuk meninjau kembali seluruh informasi sebelum mengirimkan formulir.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/20 bg-white text-primary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm">2</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Akses Kelas & Syarat Administrasi</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium mb-3">Setelah berhasil melakukan pendaftaran, Anda akan mendapatkan:</p>
                            <ul class="list-none text-subtle font-medium text-sm space-y-2">
                                <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>Akses ke Kelas Financial Literacy yang harus diselesaikan sebagai persyaratan administrasi.</li>
                                <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>Akses ke Kelas Dasar-Pemula sesuai Alur Belajar yang dipilih.</li>
                                <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>Akses ke Kelas Softskill Belajar Strategi Pengembangan Diri.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/20 bg-white text-primary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm">3</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Pengumuman Level Lanjutan</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Tahap terakhir ini akan memberikan Anda informasi mengenai hasil pengumuman di level lanjutan yang terdiri dari beberapa Batch.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- METC Process -->
            <div class="bg-surface p-6 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-subtle-light shadow-sm hover:shadow-hover-premium transition-all duration-300">
                 <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                     <div class="h-10 w-2.5 bg-secondary rounded-full"></div>
                     <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 tracking-tight">METC</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-10 relative">
                     <!-- Connection line -->
                     <div class="absolute left-[1.15rem] top-10 bottom-10 w-0.5 bg-slate-100 hidden sm:block"></div>
                     
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary/20 bg-white text-secondary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm">1</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Pendaftaran Awal</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Lakukan registrasi di halaman program METC menggunakan akun Dicoding Anda untuk menyatakan minat dan kesediaan.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary/20 bg-white text-secondary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm">2</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Undangan Aktivitas Berkala</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Sesuai dengan ketersediaan kegiatan (Self-learning, Workshop, atau Hackathon), Anda akan menerima undangan via email.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary/20 bg-white text-secondary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm">3</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Sertifikasi & Rewards</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Selesaikan misi atau event untuk mendapatkan Badge of Completion, Sertifikat, dan kesempatan memenangkan berbagai rewards.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
